        "management": "Treat underlying malignancy urgently. RT to mediastinum (especially SCLC, NSCLC, lymphoma). Chemotherapy for chemo-sensitive tumors (SCLC, lymphoma). Stenting of SVC (endovascular) for rapid relief - preferred first-line for severe symptoms. Steroids (dexamethasone) to reduce edema."
