          { "feature": "acute_symptoms", "weight": 4 },
          { "feature": "no_mediastinal_mass_on_imaging", "weight": 4 }
        ],
        "management": "Anticoagulation (heparin then warfarin/DOAC). Catheter-directed thrombolysis. SVC stenting. Consider catheter removal if infected. May require venoplasty."
      }
    ],
